---

## Evaluation Results (40 queries, top-5)

| Mode | Precision@5 | Recall@5 | MRR |
|------|------------|----------|-----|
| Vector-Only (FAISS) | 0.125 | 0.625 | 0.556 |
| Hybrid + MMR | 0.100 | 0.500 | 0.488 |

**Key finding:** Hybrid+MMR recovers sections missed by vector alone (e.g., Section 100 for "right of private defence extends to death"). Lower overall scores reflect a genuine data limitation — 75% of IPC clauses have < 100 chars due to multi-column PDF extraction difficulties.

