---

## How to Run

```powershell
cd "g:\apps\Hybrid-MMR Legal RAG Project\legal_rag"

# Full demo (5 queries, all modes)
python main.py

# Single query
python main.py --query "punishment for murder"

# Launch Streamlit UI (http://localhost:8501)
python -m streamlit run app.py

# Run evaluation (40 queries, chart saved to data/evaluation_results.png)
python main.py --eval

# Force rebuild all indices
python main.py --rebuild
```

---

## Streamlit UI Features

- 🎨 Dark glassmorphism theme
- 📋 15 example queries (dropdown)
- 🔀 3 modes: Side-by-Side | Vector-Only | Hybrid+MMR
- 🎚️ MMR λ slider (0.5–1.0) — tune live
- 📊 Score pills: Hybrid / Vector / BM25 / MMR rank
- 📖 Full section text viewer
- 📈 Evaluation chart in sidebar
